headline: Meta Connect 2025: What to expect and how to watch
summary: Meta is expected to unveil new versions of its AI-powered smart glasses, as well as a gesture-indicating wristband.

headline: Garmin celebrates global innovators and collaborations at 2025 Garmin Health Summit
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) today announced the recipients of the 2025 Garmin Health Awards. Presented at the annual Garmin Health Summit, the awards honored dynamic and forward-thinking digital health solutions utilizing Garmin smartwatches, fitness trackers and data integration.
